main event: A witness reported a stationary, white luminous object that pulsated in Kingsville, Canada on September 6, 1956.
interesting points: The object was observed for 8 minutes from 0215 to 0223,The object disappeared on the horizon heading east,No photographs are available in the report,The case is listed under Project Blue Book but the file has not been found,The sighting was made by a civilian.
